definition:
Someone descended from Ard, a man of the tribe of Benjamin living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness, only mentioned at Num.26.40; 
 son of: Bela (H1106A); 
 brother of: Naaman (H5283H), Ezbon (H0675H), Uzzi (H5813I), Uzziel (H5816I), Jerimoth (H3406), Iri (H5901), Addar (H0146H), Gera (H1617I), Abihud (H0031), Abishua (H0050H) and Ahoah (H0265)
Group of ard (אַרְדְּ "Ard" H0714H) 
 § Ardites = "I shall subdue"
 the descendants of Ard
